      <h2><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hw6s3qZT3SM">Craig Ferguson destroys moral particularism on the Letterman show</a></h2> 
      <p>I&#8217;ve never seen such an impressive educational performance on comedy TV before; bravo to Ferguson.</p>
